518
00:31:05,060 --> 00:31:05,900
She has?

519
00:31:06,820 --> 00:31:08,620
After the New Year,

520
00:31:08,620 --> 00:31:09,500
you and your mother

521
00:31:09,500 --> 00:31:10,500
