574
00:32:56,580 --> 00:32:57,420
Prof. Meng.

575
00:32:59,020 --> 00:32:59,860
There you are, Ji Xing.

576
00:33:02,180 --> 00:33:03,060
Ji Xing?

577
00:33:05,100 --> 00:33:06,260
