603
00:34:06,620 --> 00:34:07,460
Thanks.

604
00:34:09,220 --> 00:34:10,060
By the way,

605
00:34:10,060 --> 00:34:11,020
I only know

606
00:34:11,020 --> 00:34:12,820
you're a genius in AI

607
00:34:12,980 --> 00:34:14,580
