655
00:36:12,980 --> 00:36:14,380
You look calm.

656
00:36:14,780 --> 00:36:16,580
Are you preparing big moves?

657
00:36:17,500 --> 00:36:18,780
If you have too much free time,

658
00:36:19,180 --> 00:36:20,060
